Tapi sekarang...

00:19:11.961 --> 00:19:14.231
...luka-luka itu terbuka.

00:19:15.298 --> 00:19:16.655
Sekali lagi...

00:19:17.126 --> 00:19:19.903
...Trilochan Roy
Chaudhary menghinaku.

